source.name: ED Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) Annual Report - FY2010
source.description: This file contains the FY 2010 FOIA annual report of the U.S. Department of Education (ED). The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 2010. It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
